<PolicyLayout
  title="Cookie policy"
  description="The seocli.sh website does not set project-controlled cookies or run project-controlled analytics."
>
  <h1>Cookie policy</h1>
  <p>Last updated: 10 July 2026</p>
  <p>
    The seocli.sh website does not set project-controlled cookies, create
    user accounts, or run project-controlled analytics.
  </p>
  <p>
    The site is served through Cloudflare. Cloudflare may process normal web
    request data and may use strictly necessary security mechanisms under its
    own policies. The website does not receive your local SEO reports, Google
    tokens, or Google API responses.
  </p>
  <p>
    If this changes, this page and the <a href="/privacy">privacy policy</a>
    will be updated before project-controlled cookies or analytics are added.
  </p>
  <h2>Questions</h2>
  <p>
    Open an issue in the
    <a href="https://github.com/iannuttall/seo/issues">public GitHub repository</a>.
    Do not include tokens, private reports, personal data, or other secrets.
  </p>
</PolicyLayout>
